  "prompt": "How can I change my name in Clash of Clan?",
  "response": "To change your name in Clash of Clans, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Open Clash of Clans**: Launch the game on your device.\n\n2. **Access Settings**: Tap on the gear icon (Settings) located in the bottom right corner of the screen.\n\n3. **Change Name**: In the settings menu, look for the \"More Settings\" option and tap on it. Then look for the \"Change Player Name\" option.\n\n4. **Enter New Name**: You\u2019ll be prompted to enter your new name. Keep in mind that there is a character limit, and you must also comply with the game's naming rules (no offensive language, etc.).\n\n5. **Cost**: Changing your name will usually cost you 500 Gems, so make sure you have enough Gems to proceed.\n\n6. **Confirm**: After entering your new name and confirming the change, your name will be updated.\n\nRemember that you can only change your name once every 30 days, so choose wisely! Enjoy playing Clash of Clans with your new name!",
